---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Responsible AI | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="Responsible AI systems designed around transparency, assurance, governance, and professional judgement."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">Responsible AI</p>
      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        AI that supports judgement, accountability, and trust.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        PrincipalAI designs AI systems for organisations that need transparency, governance, assurance, and human oversight in high-value decision environments.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">The problem</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            AI adoption needs confidence, not only capability.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Organisations need to know how AI systems use information, where outputs come from, what assumptions matter, and where expert review remains essential.
          </p>
          <p>
            Responsible AI is not a compliance add-on. It is part of building AI systems that can be used safely and effectively in professional decision-making.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">Core principles</p>
        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Designed for transparency, review, and decision assurance.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Human oversight</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Keep expert judgement central in workflows where quality, context, and consequences matter.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Evidence grounding</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Connect AI outputs to approved documents, data, models, and analytical evidence.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Governance</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Support access control, review points, role clarity, and appropriate use of AI-enabled workflows.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Traceability</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Improve confidence through clearer provenance, citations, workflow records, and structured review.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">What it supports</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Responsible AI for high-trust environments.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            AI-assisted research, policy, regulatory, and technical advisory workflows.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Private AI systems that operate within controlled organisational environments.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Decision-support tools where outputs must be reviewed, justified, and documented.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            AI systems connected to evidence, models, data, and organisational knowledge.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">Why PrincipalAI</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Built for organisations where consequences matter.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            PrincipalAI designs systems for evidence-heavy, judgement-intensive work. Our focus is not only whether AI can produce an answer, but whether users can understand, review, and apply that answer appropriately.
          </p>
          <p>
            We combine AI capability with economics, modelling, policy, infrastructure, climate, energy, health, and geospatial expertise to support defensible decisions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Deploy AI with confidence and accountability.
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about responsible AI design, governance, assurance, and human-in-the-loop workflows.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
